'''''The Official Star Wars Fact File'' 14''' was the fourteenth issue of ''[[The Official Star Wars Fact File]]'', released on [[April 3]], [[2002]]. The issue was authored by [[Darren Allanson]], [[Chris Gardner]], and [[Iain Lowson]]. It also featured original artwork by [[Carl Lyons]].

